<p>Alf Watt, developer of iStumbler and also formerly of Apple&#39;s Wi-Fi group, joins John and Dave today to answer all of your (and their!) Wi-Fi concerns. Join these three geeks to absorb all the Wi-Fi knowledge you can. Download, press play and enjoy!</p>
